Note 1: This test was run on the HB+BP toplevel in the tapeout repository
Note 2: BP <--> HB interaction has been tested only for a single pod

Commit ID: 
tapeout repository: 2a92f08ebfdd5acfdd1ac97ba755200a5a002622

To run this test, use - 
make bsg_pods_X=1 bsg_pods_Y=1 HOST=bp

To generate a waveform dump - 
make bsg_pods_X=1 bsg_pods_Y=1 WAVE=1 HOST=bp

To build the RTL, use the instructions given in the tapeout repository
